Class Person

java.lang.Object
org.example.domain.Entity<Long>
org.example.domain.User
org.example.domain.Person
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Observer
public class Person extends User
Represents a person in the social network. A person has a surname, first name, birthdate, and occupation, in addition to the inherited User fields (id, username, email, password).
